    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you, but inflamation is basically what causes the pain, right? if i can just get the swelling down with the ice and maybe take some extra ibuprofen, it'll be way easier to move and tell if something is actually wrong. if i can walk on it by tomorrow, then it clearly isn't broken, right? i'd rather just tough it out for 48 hours than spend hundreds on a random x-ray.",
